name: Cthulhu Tote Bag
description:
Tote bag with hand-printed illustration by Jonathan Taylor of Cthulhu, a character created by H.P. Lovecraft. This bag has proven to be our best seller so far!

Material: 165gsm 100% natural bio-degradable cotton
Size: 38cm x 42cm
Handle: 32.5cm
Capacity: 15 litres

Each bag is especially prepared to order, the watermarks seen in product image will not be present on the actual product.

Please allow seven days for delivery. The bag is posted first class recorded delivery within United Kingdom. Please note that if you require delivery from outside of United Kingdom please contact us for a quote on postage before making payment.

Please note that care should be taken not to machine wash or iron the print, only if absolutely necessary hand wash the bag carefully inside out in cool water, do not to allow the item to soak.

© 2013 Fluid 67
